body: Hi Farzane. The error is an issue with downloading Honeybee libraries. See [this discussion](http://www.grasshopper3d.com/group/ladybug/forum/topics/1-solution-exception-unterminated-string-starting-at-line-1?commentId=2985220%3AComment%3A1383958&groupId=2985220%3AGroup%3A658987). You need to copy the files and then re-open your file and the error will be gone.
